Revision history for Perl module EBook::Gutenberg

1.00  May 16 2025
  - Add "menu" command: dialog-based TUI for gutenberg.
  - Default path for downloaded ebooks is now derived from the ebook title
    rather than its ID.
  - Fixed -H|--shelf searching.

0.03  May 11 2025
  - gutenberg now prints a proper usage message rather than displaying its
    manual.
  - gutenberg uses XDG_DATA_HOME and ~/.local/share as additional potential
    default data directories.

0.02  Mar 21 2025
  - Require List::Util 1.33.

0.01  Mar 11 2025
  - Initial release.
